 in Central Africa. As secretary-general, Ban also forged global agreements to fight extreme poverty and address the climate crisis.Ban performed what has been called “the most impossible job on this earth” with a genuine belief in collective action and global transformation. Freed from the diplomatic constraints of a lifetime of public service, he offers a candid assessment of the people and events that shape our era and a bracing analysis of what lies ahead.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 04. Okt 2022) 0aDiplomatszKorea (South)vBiography. 0aPoliticianszKorea (South)vBiography. 7aBIOGRAPHY & AUTOBIOGRAPHY / Political.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertColumbia University Press Complete eBook-Package 2021z978311073907708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishz978311075400108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Political Science 2021 Englishz978311075417908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Political Science 2021z9783110753943oZDB-23-PLW40uhttps://doi.org/10.7312/ban-1987240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780231552783423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780231552783/original  a978-3-11-073907-7  Columbia University Press Complete eBook-Package 2021b2021  a978-3-11-075400-1  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishb2021  a978-3-11-075417-9  EBOOK PACKAGE Political Science 2021 Englishb2021  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_SN  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2021  aZDB-23-PLWb2021